            <p>The industries that commonly spring to mind when talking about VR are computer gaming, entertainment and real estate.</p>
              <p>However the possibilities of VR technology go much further than simply enhancing what we already do. Read below for ten exciting uses that demonstrate virtual reality’s tremendous capacity and versatility for change.</p>
